half the night.

00:06:35.399 --> 00:06:36.879
I only just managed a short nap.

00:06:39.959 --> 00:06:41.600
You should prioritize the royal heir.

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:43.079
Focus on resting well.

00:06:43.759 --> 00:06:44.680
Only then,

00:06:45.079 --> 00:06:47.120
